deck: John Carpenter is a notorious horror/sci-fi movie director who is well-known for the creation of cult classics like Halloween, The Thing and Escape from New York. Recently he has started working with comics, his biggest contributions so far are Asylum and Big Trouble in Little China, the latter based in one of his most famous films.
